<item>
            <title>[SPARK-16291] Invalid aggregate functions like MAX(COUNT(*)) are not captured by CheckAnalysis</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-16291</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue can be reproduced by the following snippet:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;spark.range(1).createOrReplaceTempView(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;test&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
spark.sql(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;SELECT MAX(COUNT(*)) FROM test GROUP BY id&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;An analysis phase error report like the following is expected:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;It is not allowed to use an aggregate function in the argument of another aggregate function. ...&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, this error is not captured at analysis phase, but leads an execution time exception:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Error in SQL statement: SparkException: Job aborted due to stage failure: Task 9 in stage 355.0 failed 4 times, most recent failure: Lost task 9.3 in stage 355.0 (TID 12920, ip-10-31-224-146.ec2.internal): java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException: Cannot evaluate expression: (count(1),mode=Complete,isDistinct=false)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
